THIS APP SHOWS 
          - Display a gallery within your app
          - Add images to it via camera or phone's gallery
          - Click open an image to show the full view
          - Delete the image
          - Share it to Facebook and other social media apps.
          
          NOTE: This doesn't use Content Resolver to get the thumbnails for the grid. I am creating the thumbnails on the fly
          Please refer to app-snapshot.png to see the screenshots of the gallery app.
